                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880910-35-defend356 t17880910-35-punish161"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
